OL,6,FIn the plans to be announced by
OL,7,FMcFadden at the start of the week, he
OL,8,Fwill promise a new "mutually agreed
OL,9,Fexits" process, in which civil
OL,10,Fservants who cannot perform at the
OL,11,Flevel required of them are
OL,12,Fincentivised to leave their jobs.
OL,14,FThe system will be designed to give
OL,15,Fbosses more tools to address bad
OL,16,Fperformance.
